cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SE 

This paper deals with data storage and security in sensor networks, which involves aspects of cryptography (cs.CR), distributed systems (cs.DS), networking (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), and software engineering (cs.SE). However, since the focus is primarily on security and distributed storage, cs.CR and cs.DS are the most likely categories.
